data.description: Beautiful lake front home on Medina Lake, located in the popular Pebble Beach Subdivision. The numerous windows offer amazing views of the lake and scenic hill country.  This home features an open floor plan with a gorgeous rock fireplace to keep you warm during the colder months.  A two car garage and an abundance of storage areas throughout the property.  Multiple patios and decks to enjoy the views, wildlife, or to entertain friends and family.   Property comes with a floating dock plus a walk out basement/workshop with a full bath. The entire exterior was painted 2 years ago and the inside was updated with new flooring and paint last year.  This home features a metal roof that was recently resealed.   Note: the lake is very low due to the drought.  Pictures of water are from when the lake was up.
